OL,3,CRecord 274 climbers scale Mount
OL,4,CEverest in a single day
OL,6,FA record-breaking 272 climbers reached
OL,7,Fthe summit of Everest on the southern
OL,8,Fside of the world's highest mountain
OL,9,Fon Wednesday, taking advantage of good
OL,10,Fweather.
OL,12,FIt was the highest number of climbers
OL,13,Fto scale the peak on a single day via
OL,14,Fthe popular Nepal route. The northern
OL,15,Fface route, accessed from China's
OL,16,FTibet, has been closed by the
OL,17,Fauthorities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
