OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779401472
OL,3,CRecord 274 climbers scale Mount
OL,4,CEverest in a single day
OL,6,FThe record for the most climbers in
OL,7,Fone day is 336 when on May 22, 2019,
OL,8,Fwhen 223 climbers summited from Nepal,
OL,9,Fand 113 accessed the mountain from
OL,10,FChina.
OL,12,FIt is not the only record that has
OL,13,Fbeen broken. Earlier this week,
OL,14,Fveteran mountain guide Kami Rita
OL,15,FSherpa scaled the peak for the 32nd
OL,16,Ftime, breaking his own record.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
