OL,3,CRecord 274 climbers scale Mount
OL,4,CEverest in a single day
OL,6,FHis closest competitor, Pasang Dawa
OL,7,FSherpa, scaled the peak for the 30th
OL,8,Ftime this week. Also, Lakpa Sherpa
OL,9,Fscaled Everest for the 11th time,
OL,10,Ftopping her own record for the highest
OL,11,Fnumber of climbs by a female climber.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThis year's Everest climbing season
OL,19,Fbegan late because of the risk from a
OL,20,Fhuge serac hanging over the key route
OL,21,Fto the summit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
