PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779401472
OL,3,CRecord 274 climbers scale Mount
OL,4,CEverest in a single day
OL,6,FThere are around 494 climbers and an
OL,7,Fequal number of their Sherpa guides
OL,8,Fwho are expected to attempt to scale
OL,9,Fthe 8,850-metre (29,032-foot) peak by
OL,10,Fthe end of this month, when the
OL,11,Fclimbing season on the peak ends.
OL,13,FThousands of people have climbed the
OL,14,Fpeak since it was first scaled on May
OL,15,F29, 1953, by New Zealander Edmund
OL,16,FHillary and Sherpa guide Tenzing
OL,17,FNorgay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
